  <!-- EN:
    <li>questDescription->[asker_nameFull], [asker_faction_leaderTitle] of [asker_faction_name], has sent us a message. Apparently, [siteFaction_pawnsPlural] are resting with their beasts before continuing their journey.\n            \n[asker_nameDef] gave us their location, if we want to, we can go attack them.</li>
  -->
