  <!-- EN: The [siteFaction_pawnsPlural] packed up their stuff and moved on. The quest [resolvedQuestName] has expired. -->
  <VFES_CaravanRaid.root.nodes.WorldObjectTimeout.node.nodes.Letter.text.slateRef>[siteFaction_pawnsPlural]已经收拾好了他们的物资，继续前进了。任务[resolvedQuestName]已失效。</VFES_CaravanRaid.root.nodes.WorldObjectTimeout.node.nodes.Letter.text.slateRef>
  <!-- EN: Quest failed: [resolvedQuestName] -->
  <VFES_CaravanRaid.root.nodes.siteDestroyed.node.nodes.Letter.label.slateRef>任务失败：[resolvedQuestName]</VFES_CaravanRaid.root.nodes.siteDestroyed.node.nodes.Letter.label.slateRef>
