  <VFES_CaravanRaid.root.nodes.siteDestroyed.node.nodes.Letter.text.slateRef>在被发现后，[siteFaction_pawnsPlural]离开了。任务[resolvedQuestName]已失效。</VFES_CaravanRaid.root.nodes.siteDestroyed.node.nodes.Letter.text.slateRef>
  
  <!-- EN:
    <li>questName->Bounty: [nameFull] [nickname]</li>
    <li>questName->Wanted, Dead or Alive: [nickname]</li>
    <li>questName->[nickname]'s brigands</li>
    <li>questDescription->[asker_nameFull], [asker_faction_leaderTitle] of [asker_faction_name] hails us. Apparently, the notorious [criminal_nameFull] of [siteFaction_name] is hiding out in our vicinity.\n\n[asker_nameDef] is asking us to bring [nickname] to one of their settlements for a grand sum of [bounty] silver, double if alive. They are hiding in a safe house and it's probably guarded.\n\nIf we clear out their camp, [allRewardsDescriptions]</li>
  -->
  <VFES_Wanted.questDescriptionAndNameRules.rulesStrings>  
    <li>questName->悬赏：[nameFull][nickname]</li>
    <li>questName->通缉[nickname]：不论死活</li>
    <li>questName->缉拿[nickname]</li>
    <li>questDescription->[asker_faction_name]的[asker_faction_leaderTitle][asker_nameFull]呼叫了我们。看起来，[siteFaction_name]臭名昭著的[criminal_nameFull]正躲在我们附近。\n\n[asker_nameDef]要求我们将[nickname]带至他们的一个定居点。作为报酬，他们会支付赏金[bounty]银，如果目标活着则翻倍。[nickname]躲在一个安全屋里，且可能有护卫存在。\n\n如果我们能成功摧毁[nickname]的藏身处，[allRewardsDescriptions]</li>
  </VFES_Wanted.questDescriptionAndNameRules.rulesStrings>
