  <!-- EN: Payment arrived -->
  <VFES_Wanted.root.nodes.siteAllEnemiesDefeated.node.customLetterLabel.slateRef>奖励已送达</VFES_Wanted.root.nodes.siteAllEnemiesDefeated.node.customLetterLabel.slateRef>
  <!-- EN: You have defeated [criminal_nameFull] and eliminated the camp!\n\nThe bonus reward from [asker_faction_name] has arrived. -->
  <VFES_Wanted.root.nodes.siteAllEnemiesDefeated.node.customLetterText.slateRef>你成功击败了[criminal_nameFull]，并摧毁了藏身处！\n\n来自[asker_faction_name]的奖赏已经抵达。</VFES_Wanted.root.nodes.siteAllEnemiesDefeated.node.customLetterText.slateRef>
  
